function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	
	idShrine = idActorGizmo
	
-- Applys a knock back on the player and disables the shrine.
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idShrine, S_KNOCKBACK_POWER)
	Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(S_KNOCKBACK_POWER, "CHEST_VFX", idShrine)
	Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(S_SHRINE_DEBUFF, "Player_Debuff", idShrine)
	Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idShrine, true)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idMapIcon)
	
-- Keeps the shrine from actually activating.	
	return false
end

function Start(idActorKiller, szGroup)
	
-- Increment the wave count.	
	nWaveCount = nWaveCount + 1	
	Hydra.EventSend("WaveClear", idSelf)
	
-- Add a small pause between waves.	
	Hydra.Wait(1)

-- Spawn additional waves.
	if nWaveCount == 1 then
		
		-- Spawn Wave 2
		for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tWAVE_02) do
			if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSpawner) then
				Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawner, false)
				Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(idSpawner)
			end
		end
		
	elseif nWaveCount >= 2 then 
		
		-- Spawn Wave 3. Wave 3 will respawn until timer runs out.
		for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tWAVE_03) do
			if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSpawner) then 
				Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawner, false)
				Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(idSpawner)
			end
		end
	end
	

end

function Start(listValidActors, idActorDetector)

-- While the player is inside the trigger they will be given a debuff that removes health over time.
	for i, idPlayer in ipairs(listValidActors) do
		Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(S_SHRINE_DEBUFF, "Player_Debuff", idPlayer)
	end
	
end
